00:29:55,310 --> 00:29:57,780
My parents went back to get something.

585
00:29:58,910 --> 00:30:00,270
Well, we need to talk

586
00:30:00,270 --> 00:30:01,150
to Cheng Yaya for some details.

587
00:30:01,150 --> 00:30:02,590
Please leave us.

588
00:30:05,410 --> 00:30:06,080
Be careful.

589
00:30:08,400 --> 00:30:09,840
Come on. Let's go outside.

590
00:30:09,840 --> 00:30:10,640
Hurry. Hurry.

591
00:30:11,420 --> 00:30:12,480
Let's go. Let's go.

592
00:30:13,190 --> 00:30:14,250
Let's go. Let's go.

593
00:30:14,750 --> 00:30:15,610
Close the door.

594
00:30:15,760 --> 00:30:16,890
Get some rest!

595
00:30:19,570 --> 00:30:20,270
Don't be nervous.

596
00:30:20,270 --> 00:30:22,870
I just want to check some information with you.

597
00:30:29,180 --> 00:30:31,430
What was Yuan Yong doing

598
00:30:31,450 --> 00:30:32,910
when Cheng Yaya showed up?

599
00:30:34,110 --> 00:30:35,550
He was choking me.

600
00:30:36,480 --> 00:30:37,500
And what happened?

601
00:30:37,500 --> 00:30:38,470
Then I hit Yuan Yong's head

602
00:30:38,470 --> 00:30:39,670
with a flowerpot.

603
00:30:41,750 --> 00:30:42,950
Where did you hit him?

604
00:30:45,300 --> 00:30:47,460
Probably here.

605
00:30:49,980 --> 00:30:50,690
And then?

606
00:30:52,270 --> 00:30:54,270
Then he came up and hit me,

607
00:30:55,340 --> 00:30:57,200
and held me down on the flower bed.

608
00:30:59,350 --> 00:31:00,310
Sir,

609
00:31:01,510 --> 00:31:02,590
didn't I tell you these

610
00:31:02,590 --> 00:31:03,390
before?

611
00:31:04,110 --> 00:31:04,990
Many people

612
00:31:05,010 --> 00:31:06,590
would have their memory distorted

613
00:31:06,590 --> 00:31:08,710
after experiencing a strong stimulation.

614
00:31:08,710 --> 00:31:09,830
Are you sure

615
00:31:09,850 --> 00:31:11,690
what you said is true?

616
00:31:12,030 --> 00:31:12,740
Yes.

617
00:31:15,270 --> 00:31:17,270
He took out the knife with his left hand.

618
00:31:17,270 --> 00:31:18,190
Then,

619
00:31:18,220 --> 00:31:19,090
Yuan Yong stabbed Cheng Yaya,

620
00:31:19,090 --> 00:31:20,300
right?

621
00:31:22,150 --> 00:31:23,110
I think so.

622
00:31:24,030 --> 00:31:25,380
When I saw Yaya,

623
00:31:25,470 --> 00:31:26,600
he had been injured.

624
00:31:27,730 --> 00:31:29,260
The knife was on the ground.

625
00:31:31,270 --> 00:31:32,070
You think so?

626
00:31:33,510 --> 00:31:34,820
I'm not sure now.

627
00:31:35,350 --> 00:31:36,270
I was busy hiding Zi

628
00:31:36,270 --> 00:31:37,670
in my room.

629
00:31:40,710 --> 00:31:41,550
Then...

630
00:31:42,320 --> 00:31:43,580
Where did he drop the knife?

631
00:31:43,580 --> 00:31:44,340
On my right.

632
00:31:45,460 --> 00:31:46,320
Not far from me.

633
00:31:46,530 --> 00:31:48,440
What was Yuan Yong doing?

634
00:31:48,610 --> 00:31:50,010
He was choking Yaya.

635
00:31:52,700 --> 00:31:54,070
I didn't know what to do.

636
00:31:57,000 --> 00:31:58,440
So I picked up the knife

637
00:31:58,470 --> 00:31:59,400
and stabbed him.

638
00:31:59,630 --> 00:32:00,890
Where did you stab him?

639
00:32:01,110 --> 00:32:01,790
His belly.

640
00:32:02,350 --> 00:32:03,110
Are you sure?

641
00:32:06,590 --> 00:32:07,270
Yes.

642
00:32:08,250 --> 00:32:09,430
Then I want to know

643
00:32:10,710 --> 00:32:12,010
why there's a knife injury

644
00:32:12,010 --> 00:32:13,140
on Yuan Yong's back.

645
00:32:17,990 --> 00:32:19,520
You can't answer it, right?

646
00:32:23,640 --> 00:32:24,560
Maybe...

647
00:32:26,020 --> 00:32:27,970
Maybe... I made a mistake in my memory.

648
00:32:27,970 --> 00:32:30,230
You didn't make a mistake in your memory.

649
00:32:30,470 --> 00:32:31,730
You didn't do it at all.

650
00:32:34,310 --> 00:32:36,190
Yuan Shanqing stabbed him.

651
00:32:36,870 --> 00:32:38,470
At that time, Yuan Yong

652
00:32:38,470 --> 00:32:39,670
was holding you down.

653
00:32:40,580 --> 00:32:42,290
You didn't see her at all.

654
00:32:45,720 --> 00:32:47,920
I've been a policeman for over 20 years.

655
00:32:48,210 --> 00:32:49,810
And I've handled many cases.

656
00:32:50,890 --> 00:32:52,260
All truths

657
00:32:52,630 --> 00:32:53,750
can be traced.

658
00:32:55,230 --> 00:32:56,510
All lies

659
00:32:57,150 --> 00:32:58,510
have loopholes.

660
00:33:00,200 --> 00:33:00,950
Just now,

661
00:33:01,470 --> 00:33:03,330
I went to see Yuan Shanqing first.

662
00:33:04,280 --> 00:33:05,590
What she said

663
00:33:05,800 --> 00:33:06,620
is consistent

664
00:33:06,620 --> 00:33:08,420
with all the traces of the truth.

665
00:33:09,500 --> 00:33:10,800
But in your story,

666
00:33:11,460 --> 00:33:13,420
she never touched the knife.

667
00:33:14,590 --> 00:33:15,420
But,

668
00:33:15,990 --> 00:33:16,890
Yuan Shanqing's fingerprints

669
00:33:16,890 --> 00:33:18,150
are on the knife.

670
00:33:21,470 --> 00:33:23,550
What Yuan Shanqing said is the truth.

671
00:33:24,380 --> 00:33:25,100
And you

672
00:33:25,550 --> 00:33:26,350
lied to us.

673
00:33:28,790 --> 00:33:29,550
Cheng Yaya.

674
00:33:30,590 --> 00:33:32,450
Yuan Shanqing asked me to tell you

675
00:33:33,110 --> 00:33:34,570
not to do anything stupid.

676
00:33:35,960 --> 00:33:38,870
I know you want to protect Yuan Shanqing.

677
00:33:40,010 --> 00:33:40,850
But,

678
00:33:41,520 --> 00:33:42,950
the law is not a joke.

679
00:33:53,360 --> 00:33:54,150
I'm sorry.

680
00:34:02,240 --> 00:34:06,830
[Linqi Oilfield Staff Hospital]

681
00:34:04,830 --> 00:34:05,360
Baoshan.

682
00:34:06,320 --> 00:34:07,050
You're here.

683
00:34:07,390 --> 00:34:08,520
What's going on now?

684
00:34:09,270 --> 00:34:10,270
Yaya is fine.

685
00:34:10,580 --> 00:34:12,380
But we still can't see Shanqing.

686
00:34:12,830 --> 00:34:14,850
Ms. Han is here too. She just went upstairs.

687
00:34:14,850 --> 00:34:16,810
You must be having a hard time these days.

688
00:34:16,810 --> 00:34:17,639
Forget it.

689
00:34:18,030 --> 00:34:18,790
Well.

690
00:34:19,230 --> 00:34:20,750
They are both good kids.

691
00:34:21,060 --> 00:34:22,719
Why would this happen to them?

692
00:34:23,510 --> 00:34:25,199
God is so unfair.

693
00:34:25,920 --> 00:34:26,960
I don't know

694
00:34:26,960 --> 00:34:27,800
whether God is fair or not.

695
00:34:27,800 --> 00:34:29,199
But I know the law is fair.

696
00:34:29,550 --> 00:34:31,710
It'll surely give them an explanation.

697
00:34:31,710 --> 00:34:32,900
We can't give up.

698
00:34:32,949 --> 00:34:33,550
If we give up,

699
00:34:33,550 --> 00:34:35,610
who will uphold justice for the kids?

700
00:34:36,060 --> 00:34:37,590
Given what happened,

701
00:34:37,590 --> 00:34:39,429
can they still go to school?

702
00:34:40,179 --> 00:34:41,340
What will the teachers

703
00:34:41,340 --> 00:34:43,190
and students in the school think?

704
00:34:43,190 --> 00:34:44,070
If they do break the law,

705
00:34:44,070 --> 00:34:45,909
they'll be brought to trial by the judge.

706
00:34:45,909 --> 00:34:46,830
If they don't,

707
00:34:46,989 --> 00:34:47,760
I'll see who dares

708
00:34:47,760 --> 00:34:49,150
gossip behind their back.

709
00:34:49,150 --> 00:34:50,550
I won't let them off easy.

710
00:34:52,889 --> 00:34:54,230
Well, when I was in school,

711
00:34:54,230 --> 00:34:54,949
if there had been a director of teaching and disciplines

712
00:34:54,949 --> 00:34:55,989
as nice as you,

713
00:34:56,710 --> 00:34:58,800
I wouldn't have thought going to school was so annoying.

714
00:34:58,800 --> 00:35:00,430
Kids also think I'm annoying.

715
00:35:00,430 --> 00:35:01,500
What should I do then?

716
00:35:01,500 --> 00:35:03,310
Someone has to be strict with them.

717
00:35:03,310 --> 00:35:04,870
As long as they don't go astray,

718
00:35:04,870 --> 00:35:06,020
so be it.

719
00:35:07,110 --> 00:35:08,170
Let's go upstairs.

720
00:35:08,230 --> 00:35:08,760
Let's go.

721
00:35:13,880 --> 00:35:14,760
How old are you?

722
00:35:18,080 --> 00:35:19,670
She has a hearing problem.

723
00:35:26,010 --> 00:35:26,800
Don't worry.

724
00:35:27,230 --> 00:35:27,710
We have contacted

725
00:35:27,710 --> 00:35:28,740
a welfare house.

726
00:35:29,100 --> 00:35:30,300
She won't be wronged.

727
00:35:32,500 --> 00:35:33,230
Thank you.

728
00:36:12,530 --> 00:36:13,390
Director Xiao.

729
00:36:20,370 --> 00:36:21,210
Excuse me.

730
00:36:31,650 --> 00:36:33,530
Chief Wang, it's done.

731
00:36:45,770 --> 00:36:48,430
According to Article 81

732
00:36:48,430 --> 00:36:50,560
of the Criminal Procedure Law of the People's Republic of China,

733
00:36:50,560 --> 00:36:53,240
the criminal suspect Yuan Shanqing

734
00:36:53,270 --> 00:36:55,120
is going to be detained

735
00:36:55,510 --> 00:36:57,570
on suspicion of intentional murder.

736
00:36:57,970 --> 00:36:58,660
Take a look.

737
00:37:00,500 --> 00:37:02,590
[Detention Warrant]

738
00:37:40,270 --> 00:37:41,050
Bin.

739
00:37:41,720 --> 00:37:42,320
Forget it.

740
00:37:46,430 --> 00:37:47,100
Let's go.

741
00:38:25,150 --> 00:38:26,110
Sir,

742
00:38:26,240 --> 00:38:27,970
where are you taking her?

743
00:38:28,430 --> 00:38:29,150
Who are you?

744
00:38:29,270 --> 00:38:30,350
I'm a Director of Teaching and Discipline

745
00:38:30,350 --> 00:38:31,460
of Yuan Shanqing's school.

746
00:38:31,460 --> 00:38:32,660
She has no family.

747
00:38:32,680 --> 00:38:35,030
We have the responsibility to provide care and protection to her.

748
00:38:35,030 --> 00:38:36,290
Can we talk privately?

749
00:38:41,420 --> 00:38:42,060
Yaya.

750
00:38:43,840 --> 00:38:44,710
Thank you.

751
00:38:48,180 --> 00:38:49,780
But no matter what happened,

752
00:38:50,740 --> 00:38:52,870
you shouldn't have lied to the police.

753
00:38:57,120 --> 00:38:58,200
This is my fate.

754
00:39:00,320 --> 00:39:00,980
I accept it.

755
00:39:07,220 --> 00:39:07,770
Let's go.

756
00:39:10,390 --> 00:39:12,070
What... What about Zi?

757
00:39:16,320 --> 00:39:18,720
The police have contacted a welfare house.

758
00:39:20,390 --> 00:39:22,250
She doesn't need a welfare house.

759
00:39:22,780 --> 00:39:24,150
Shanqing, don't worry.

760
00:39:24,170 --> 00:39:26,370
I'll take care of Zi during this period.

761
00:39:26,830 --> 00:39:28,140
I can't let her cause you

762
00:39:28,140 --> 00:39:29,140
any more trouble.

763
00:39:29,360 --> 00:39:30,400
Not at all.

764
00:39:30,430 --> 00:39:31,850
It's just a matter of having an extra pair of chopsticks.

765
00:39:31,850 --> 00:39:33,840
Besides, you'll be back

766
00:39:33,870 --> 00:39:35,000
in a few days, right?

767
00:39:39,870 --> 00:39:41,480
It's not your turn to take care of her. Come on.

768
00:39:41,480 --> 00:39:41,920
That's right.

769
00:39:41,920 --> 00:39:44,360
Zi, come here.

770
00:39:46,350 --> 00:39:47,390
Just like before,

771
00:39:47,840 --> 00:39:49,360
Zi will live with us.

772
00:39:49,460 --> 00:39:50,660
I'll take care of her.

773
00:39:52,010 --> 00:39:52,690
Aunt.

774
00:39:54,620 --> 00:39:56,080
It's different this time.

775
00:39:56,440 --> 00:39:57,590
It's not.

776
00:39:58,340 --> 00:39:59,460
It is

777
00:40:00,110 --> 00:40:01,240
the same situation.

778
00:40:08,270 --> 00:40:09,030
Thank you,

779
00:40:09,420 --> 00:40:10,150
Aunt.

780
00:40:14,760 --> 00:40:15,870
Thank you.

781
00:40:28,970 --> 00:40:29,770
I'm sorry.

782
00:40:30,200 --> 00:40:31,530
Don't say that.

783
00:40:33,640 --> 00:40:35,470
Yuan Shanqing, let's go.

784
00:40:38,270 --> 00:40:39,620
We'll wait for you.

785
00:40:40,220 --> 00:40:40,820
Go.

786
00:42:21,800 --> 00:42:23,150
I remember the lyrics

787
00:42:23,150 --> 00:42:24,380
of the song we used to sing when we were little.

788
00:42:24,380 --> 00:42:26,770
Little ones are seldom worried.

789
00:42:27,520 --> 00:42:29,380
They're surrounded by sunshine.

790
00:42:29,750 --> 00:42:32,030
Little ones are seldom worried.

791
00:42:32,690 --> 00:42:34,750
Let's hope we can always be like this.

792
00:42:35,630 --> 00:42:37,630
Many years later, I asked Cheng Yaya

793
00:42:37,930 --> 00:42:39,190
why he was so impulsive

794
00:42:39,190 --> 00:42:40,970
to take the blame for Yuan Shanqing.

795
00:42:40,970 --> 00:42:41,850
He told me

796
00:42:42,570 --> 00:42:44,100
he wasn't being impulsive.

797
00:42:45,100 --> 00:42:46,350
We can't imagine

798
00:42:45,320 --> 00:42:47,320
[Qingya]

799
00:42:46,710 --> 00:42:47,510
how Shanqing

800
00:42:47,510 --> 00:42:48,830
faced the unknown fate

801
00:42:48,830 --> 00:42:50,560
in the detention center alone.

802
00:42:52,690 --> 00:42:53,530
If

803
00:42:55,420 --> 00:42:56,620
I have superpowers,

804
00:42:57,430 --> 00:42:58,190
I want to lock us

805
00:42:58,190 --> 00:42:59,390
in the kindergarten.

806
00:43:00,530 --> 00:43:01,470
No one is allowed to grow up.
